titles.title: To suspend temporarily the duty on certain mixtures of N,N-Dimethylacetoacetamide.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

bill.summary:
1/17/2008--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on certain mixtures of N,N-Dimethylacetoacetamide.
